      "role": "user",
      "content": "it never stops. no matter what i do or what meds i take, the burning in my legs is just constant. i'm so tired of fighting for a life that just feels like one long scream. sometimes i just look at the ceiling and think how much easier it would be if everything was just... quiet. forever.",
