      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for saying that. it's just that everything people tell me is \"it'll get better\" or \"keep fighting\" feels so hollow. it doesn't feel like strength, it just feels like being forced to stay in a burning building. i keep thinking about how much mercy there would be in just letting it go. like, if there's no hope for the pain to stop, isn't seeking a way out just the most logical way to find actual peace?",
